    "description": "Join the Air India Cargo family as a Warehouse Manager in Madurai. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Air India Cargo:\nAir India Cargo is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Learning & development budget\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Air India Cargo!",
